可以把计算好的总数放在title里面。       
```js
title: {
          text: `合计\n${total.toFixed(2)}万`,
          textStyle: {
            color: "#fff",
            fontSize: 20,
          },
          x: "center",
          y: "center"
        },
```

@AntonyXuX echarts 对象在外面保存就是了
```js
var chart = echarts.init(...);
chart.setOption({
   // 这里 chart 就是图表对象
});
```

`normal` can be ignored since ECharts 4.0, but it also works if there is `normal` to compat ECharts 3. Here's an example, `fontSize` works with or without `normal`.
```js
option = {
    xAxis: {},
    yAxis: {},
    series: [{
        symbolSize: 20,
        data: [
            [10.0, 8.04],
            [8.0, 6.95]
        ],
        type: 'scatter',
        label: {
            show: true, 
            fontSize: 30
        }
    }]
};
```

